{
  "stem": "9725.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When footsteps approached he was-- my mother insisted that you go-- he goes into the wardrobe so that they didn't see him, after-- particularly after Arthur left.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And after he left, my mother didn't make his bed for quite a few days to keep the imprint of his head on the pillow.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think the truth was driven home to me very, very forcefully.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] He left in, in October, and I think in November came the first-- we didn't know where he went and there were all kinds of, of rumors, you know.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said he was going-- that they were going to the interior of Poland to build up what was destroyed by the war.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But actually they were taken to the interior of Poland to the bank of the river San, which separated us from the Russian occupied part.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they pursued by bullets.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Those who were good swimmers swam across.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was an excellent swimmer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so late in the year, which was very cold, he swam.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Oh, I should have mentioned that my, my aunt, my father's sister, did come back with her son and daughter and my, my cousin David.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And Arthur and David were together on the transport.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My aunt then left with her daughter to go to the place where they had lived before.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So she didn't stay with us too long.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But my br-- Arthur and David went together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And after that we got the first notice that we would have to leave our homes with 20 pounds of our belongings.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And my mother was very ill.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She must have suffered a total nervous breakdown because she was a bit incoherent.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She was calling for my brother.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
